{"tid":852812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本便利店以簡體字列 6 大規條！網民：抵制中國 7-11 啦","createTime":"2018-10-08T06:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T08:47:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dfa92afdfd844c52d77ae1c568e2969dca53ad52","tid":852812,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2175000/2177830/jp02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2175000%2F2177830%2Fjp02--_1024.jpg&h=a908a065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本在中國内地十一黃金周成爲内地遊客最想旅遊國家，可說是完全無懼天災，但對日本人來説就未必是一件好事。畢竟兩地有文化差異，並不是所有内地遊客都會遵守日本人的規則。近日，有人就在日本便利店外發現一張以簡體字寫成的 6 大規條，很快就在網上瘋傳！<br />\n<br />\n有網民在 Facebook 群組「PLAY HARD 玩硬」出帖，表示在日本神奈川一間 7-11 便利店見到一張由 4 張 A4 紙拼接而成的超大告示。告示放在便利店的門口，當中以簡體字寫明對象是「各位中國來的遊客」，並加上 6 大規條。包括：「不要大聲講話」、「結帳要排成一線」、「不要亂放商品」、「結帳前不要吃喝商品」等，最後更誠懇地表示「非常抱歉給您帶來很多不便」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言笑說：「首先要班蝗識字」、「日本人修養真係好，對住呢啲生番都可以保持禮儀」、「會跟指示做就唔係中國人啦，叫佢排隊仲要_返你轉頭」、「每一張告示都表示佢地瀨左無數次野」、「去到邊都令人黑人憎」、「去日本好驚比人誤會係大陸人」、「香港人在日本真係要做好自己，恐怕將來會在旁加多一張寫來自香港的顧客們了」、「震驚了 13 億人的玻璃心」、「一陣又有玻璃碎，中國 7-11 又比人抵制」。不過，日本貼出簡體字告示「提醒」中國遊客守規則並不是新鮮事，大家都開始習慣了吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2175000/2177830/jp1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2175000%2F2177830%2Fjp1_600.jpg&h=1fedc164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2177830/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%97%E4%BB%A5%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%E5%88%97%206%20%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A2%9D%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%98%B2%EF%BC%9A%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%207-11%20%E5%95%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2177830%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%2588%2597%25206%2520%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A2%259D%25EF%25BC%2581%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2598%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25207-11%2520%25E5%2595%25A6&d=R5Po8f5GjK4hF73s51MjnviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=df5299e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2177830/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%97%E4%BB%A5%E7%B0%A1%E9%AB%94%E5%AD%97%E5%88%97%206%20%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A2%9D%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%98%B2%EF%BC%9A%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%207-11%20%E5%95%A6</a>"},{"pid":"31db4a67fc14d2e1464fc75c667eb33edb601f60","tid":852812,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0818288448dbacfa6fc6b6b527d7f156c9a0e9aa","tid":852812,"uid":37399,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"生番就係生番<br />\n永遠都受人鄙視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523151042224e5c153014f20c3b96acca8cd1227","tid":852812,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"乜牠們識字嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70d67fb4d0463ce01b54801e437397c3a7c9994","tid":852812,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:49:17.000Z","msg":"終割人係無得管架"},{"pid":"c9dc4c77a4a5677e7f0d97ce1aefedb9ea90838f","tid":852812,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"唔寫華人與狗不得內進，咪算畀面你囉"},{"pid":"1eadabebd133ced52eb7c1041cd792f6d744de54","tid":852812,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB